Controle types 

Prevent = proactive measuers (Firewall)

Deter = Discourage (A lock, a sign)

Detect = see it happen (Security cam, IDS)  

Corrective = Midagate damage/fix the damage.

Compensating = use a bad system but add something on top to do your best (vpn on top of wpa2 instead of just wpa3) 

Directive = Policy  



